charges.charge_disposition: Defendant sentenced to period of probation for 3 years on one count felony information. Court imposes $50 penalty assessment. While on probation, defendant not to commit any further state or federal crimes; defendant to provide Probation with any requested financial inforamtion; defendant not to open any new lines of credit without prior Probation approval; defendant to cooperate with the IRS and pay any taxes, interest and/or penalties due. Restitution not ordered due to finacial circumstance. Fine waived. (1)
